body_html:
FYI I just merged the recent changes to the branch (shown earlier in this comment thread), and now all presubmits have passed. None of the changes that were merged should have affected the build_docs_test, but then again, this PR shouldn't have affected build_docs_test in the first place. ;)

I'm merging this in, since it fixes TF 1.12 presubmits. Or at least it enables them to pass at least some of the time; we can investigate the weird build_docs_test separately.
